廣泛來說，太陽花學運是指從2014年3月18日起，因為佔領立法院而爆發的[[政治運動|政治運動]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/22/what-was-the-sunflower-movement/ |title = An Introduction to the Sunflower Movement |author =  |date = 2017-07-22 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-01-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220108052007/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/22/what-was-the-sunflower-movement/ }}</ref>，由學生和民間團體共同發起行動<ref name = "Austin Ramzy 02"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://tw.news.appledaily.com/politics/realtime/20140320/363204/ |title = 【直擊】警提升府維安　對戰一觸即發 |author =  |date = 2014-03-20 |publisher = 《[[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果日報]]》 |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2020-05-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200507004727/https://tw.news.appledaily.com/politics/realtime/20140320/363204/ }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://focustaiwan.tw/news/aipl/201403180044.aspx |title = Protesters break police line, storm Legislature |author = Tseng Ying-yu和Elizabeth Hsu |date = 2014-03-18 |publisher = [[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-09-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190909082853/http://focustaiwan.tw/news/aipl/201403180044.aspx |dead-url = no }}</ref>{{sfnm|港千尋|2015年|1loc=第26頁至第27頁}}。傳播媒體大多稱呼這次佔領立法院的行動為「太陽花學運」<ref name = "中央研究院 01">{{Cite web |url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180704105157/http://ios20.asdc.tw/e4_sunflower/ |title = 這不是太陽花「學運」 |author =  |date = 2015-10-13 |publisher = [[中央研究院|中央研究院]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  }}</ref>，抗議者還將[[向日葵|向日葵]]視為「希望」的象徵<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-26679496 |title = Rally backs Taiwan students occupying parliament |author =  |date = 2014-03-21 |publisher = [[英國廣播公司新聞網|英國廣播公司新聞網]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502093102/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-26679496 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160201222923/https://www.lagranepoca.com/archivo/31510-movimiento-girasol-taiwan-parte-1.html |title = El movimiento girasol de Taiwán (Parte 1) |author = Yiyuan Zhou和Renate Lilge-Stodieck |date = 2014-04-14 |publisher = 《[[大紀元時報|大紀元時報]]》 |language = es |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  }}</ref>，或者是代表需要陽光進入黑箱作業的運動精神<ref name = "Mark Harrison 01">{{Cite web |url = https://www.thechinastory.org/2014/04/the-sunflower-movement-in-taiwan/ |title = The Sunflower Movement in Taiwan |author = Mark Harrison |date = 2014-04-18 |publisher = The China Story |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502055041/https://www.thechinastory.org/2014/04/the-sunflower-movement-in-taiwan/ |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>{{Sfnm|黃恐龍|2014年|1loc=第53頁至第55頁|晏山農等|2015年|2loc=第173頁至第174頁|港千尋|2015年|3loc=第26頁、第88頁至第89頁、第240頁至第241頁}}。不過「太陽花學運」這個名字是偶然的命名，「太陽花」是從英語單詞「Sunflower」[[借譯|借譯]]而成，通常會以「向日葵」來稱呼<ref name = "Mark Harrison 01"/>{{sfnm|晏山農等|2015年|1loc=第8頁至第9頁}}。

最初在3月18日晚間，由於不知名人士贈送向日葵到立法院議場，隨後佔領人士便不經意地把向日葵插在議場的講臺上{{Sfnm|黃恐龍|2014年|1loc=第51頁至第53頁|晏山農等|2015年|2loc=第8頁|港千尋|2015年|3loc=第124頁至第128頁、第240頁至第241頁}}。這被推測是基於過往「[[權力歸花兒|權力歸花兒]]」的口號想像，才會使用向日葵來表現出和平精神<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140407071610/http://petrotimes.vn/news/vn/quoc-te/cach-mang-mau-sap-dien-ra-tai-dai-loan.html |title = Cách mạng màu sắp diễn ra tại Đài Loan? |author = S.Phương |date = 2014-04-01 |publisher = petrotimes.vn |language = vi |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  }}</ref>。不過參與運動的成員在裝飾著向日葵的講臺上發言的影像，在透過眾多傳播媒體流傳後，反而造成群眾送來更多的向日葵至立法院現場{{Sfnm|黃恐龍|2014年|1loc=第51頁至第53頁|港千尋|2015年|2loc=第88頁至第99頁、第124頁至第128頁、第240頁至第241頁}}。當中更有花店老闆自己準備1,000朵向日葵，分送給立法院議場內外的抗議學生與群眾打氣<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://tw.news.yahoo.com/占領立院-花店老闆送-希望-向日葵給抗議學生-群眾-022622705.html |title = 占領立院 花店老闆送「希望」向日葵給抗議學生、群眾 |author = 胡健森 |date = 2014-03-20 |publisher = [[雅虎新聞|雅虎新聞]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-04-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220409115101/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%A0%E9%A0%98%E7%AB%8B%E9%99%A2-%E8%8A%B1%E5%BA%97%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E9%80%81-%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B-%E5%90%91%E6%97%A5%E8%91%B5%E7%B5%A6%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F-%E7%BE%A4%E7%9C%BE-022622705.html }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140329100239/https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20140321/12033438.html |title = 花店老闆捐「太陽花」 盼照亮學運 |author = 張卓婷和吳宗哲 |date = 2014-03-21 |publisher = [[新浪|新浪]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  }}</ref>，傳播媒體因此逐漸以「太陽花學運」稱呼這次佔領行動{{Sfnm|劉定綱|2014年|1loc=第19頁|公民聲音團隊|2014年|2loc=第6頁|黃恐龍|2014年|3loc=第15頁|晏山農等|2015年|4loc=第8頁、第173頁至第174頁|港千尋|2015年|5loc=第88頁至第89頁、第124頁至第128頁、第240頁至第241頁}}。

「太陽花學運」這個名稱的選擇，其實也借鑿臺灣社會運動的歷史，特別是過往[[臺灣學生運動|學生運動]]的歷史<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/20/why-sunflowers/ |title = Why Sunflowers? |author =  |date = 2017-07-20 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523170108/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/20/why-sunflowers/ }}</ref>{{sfnm|港千尋|2015年|1loc=第128頁}}。實際上，太陽花學運經常被拿來和[[臺灣歷史|臺灣歷史]]上的社會運動相互比較<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/24/sunflower-history-past-movements/ |title = Relation To History In The Sunflower Movement |author =  |date = 2017-07-24 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523182232/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/24/sunflower-history-past-movements/ }}</ref>，特別是被視為1990年[[野百合學運|野百合學運]]的回應，當時的野百合學運便成功促進[[臺灣民主化|臺灣民主化]]的進程發展<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160313032847/http://www.chinapost.com.tw/commentary/the-china-post/joe-hung/2014/03/24/403513/Echoes-of.htm |title = Echoes of the Wild Lily Movement |author = Joe Hhung |date = 2014-03-24 |publisher = 《[[英文中國郵報|英文中國郵報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  }}</ref>{{sfnm|黃恐龍|2014年|1loc=第51頁至第53頁|晏山農等|2015年|2loc=第15頁至第16頁|港千尋|2015年|3loc=第83頁、第128頁|吳叡人等|2016年|4loc=第326頁}}。不過部份參與人士並不喜歡「太陽花學運」這個名稱的意涵，堅持稱呼這次佔領行動為「318佔領立法院行動」，而其他相關的名稱還有像是「318學運」、「佔領國會事件」<ref name = "小檔">{{Cite web |url = https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/paper/1331814 |title = 《小檔案》太陽花學運 反對強行通過兩岸服貿協議 |author = 郭安家 |date = 2019-11-14 |publisher = 《[[自由時報|自由時報]]》 |language =  |accessdate =  |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-11-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191114161248/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/paper/1331814 |dead-url = no }}</ref>、「向日葵運動」、「318公民運動」等{{Sfnm|公民聲音團隊|2014年|1loc=第6頁|港千尋|2015年|2loc=第124頁至第128頁}}。

