e-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502075718/https://www.zaobao.com.sg/realtime/china/story20140323-324167 |dead-url = no }}</ref>{{sfnm|黃恐龍|2014年|1loc=第182頁至第183頁|晏山農等|2015年|2loc=第54頁至第58頁|港千尋|2015年|3loc=第242頁|吳叡人等|2016年|4loc=第130頁、第192頁}}。在江宜樺下令強制驅離後，警方從隔日凌晨0時起發動六波強制驅散、逮捕的清場行動<ref name = "吳介民 01"/>，學生與民眾遭到[[警察暴力|暴力驅離]]<ref name = "中央研究院 01"/>{{sfnm|公民聲音團隊|2014年|1loc=第8頁|黃恐龍|2014年|2loc=第182頁至第183頁|晏山農等|2015年|3loc=第59頁至第61頁、第337頁|港千尋|2015年|4loc=第242頁、第192頁}}。清晨5時，警方已經全面驅離佔領行政院院區的抗議者<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.europe-solidaire.org/spip.php?article31652 |title = “Sunflower Revolution” in Taiwan : STOP Police Brutality, NO to Free Trade Agreements NOW! |author =  |date = 2014-04-14 |publisher = Europe Solidaire Sans Frontières |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-01-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220108061648/http://www.europe-solidaire.org/spip.php?article31652 }}</ref>，不過一度仍有人堅持聚集在[[忠孝東路|忠孝東路]]上<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://focustaiwan.tw/news/asoc/201403240009.aspx |title = Executive Yuan protesters dispersed with water cannons |author = Chen Chi-chung、Yuris Ku和James Lee |date = 2015-03-24 |publisher = [[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502110446/http://focustaiwan.tw/news/asoc/201403240009.aspx |dead-url = no }}</ref>{{sfnm|黃恐龍|2014年|1loc=第182頁至第183頁|晏山農等|2015年|2loc=第61頁}}。最終這次驅離行動共造成150多名抗議參與者和警察流血受傷<ref name = "中央研究院 02"/><ref name = "吳介民 01"/><ref name = "Sophie Brown 02"/><ref name = "Lawrence Chung 01">{{Cite web |url = https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/1455773/taipei-student-protesters-occupy-government-hq-ransack-cabinet-office |title = More than 150 injured as police evict student protesters from Taiwan parliament |author = Lawrence Chung |date = 2014-03-24 |publisher = 《[[南華早報|南華早報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502105714/https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/1455773/taipei-student-protesters-occupy-government-hq-ransack-cabinet-office |dead-url = no }}</ref>，部份人士則被送往國立臺灣大學醫學院附設醫院救治<ref name = "沈茂华 01"/>{{sfnm|劉定綱|2014年|1loc=第20頁|公民聲音團隊|2014年|2loc=第8頁|港千尋|2015年|3loc=第28頁、第242頁|吳叡人等|2016年|4loc=第130頁}}。

