在太陽花學運發生前，許多國際專家預測中華民國面臨中華人民共和國併吞並不會作任何抵抗，並抱持著絕望的態度，甚至有「向臺灣說再見」的命定論論點<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/24/against-say-goodbye-to-taiwan/ |title = Did The Sunflower Movement Disprove “Say Goodbye To Taiwan”? |author =  |date = 2017-07-24 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523180714/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/24/against-say-goodbye-to-taiwan/ }}</ref>{{sfnm|晏山農等|2015年|1loc=第326頁|吳叡人等|2016年|2loc=第119頁至第122頁}}。2014年3月19日，[[國際特赦組織|國際特赦組織]]發表聲明，敦促警方採取克制態度<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.amnesty.org.uk/press-releases/taiwan-restraint-urged-protests-over-china-trade-deal |title = Taiwan: Restraint urged in protests over China trade deal |author =  |date = 2014-03-19 |publisher = [[國際特赦組織|國際特赦組織]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502091622/https://www.amnesty.org.uk/press-releases/taiwan-restraint-urged-protests-over-china-trade-deal |dead-url = no }}</ref>。由臺灣網友在[[白宮|白宮]]請願網站「[[我們人民|我們人民]]」發起的反對《海峽兩岸服務貿易協議》連署，也在3月23日突破10萬人的回覆門檻<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.zaobao.com.sg/realtime/china/story20140323-324148|title=白宫网站反服贸联署 已达回覆门槛|author=明永昌|date=2014-03-23|publisher=《[[聯合早報|聯合早報]]》|language=Zh-hans|accessdate=2019-03-01|quote=|archive-date=2019-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502085740/https://www.zaobao.com.sg/realtime/china/story20140323-324148|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{sfnm|公民聲音團隊|2014年|1loc=第8頁}}。3月24日，[[美國國務院|美國國務院]]副發言人[[瑪麗·哈夫|瑪麗·哈夫]]表示，由台灣自行決定《海峽兩岸服務貿易協議》有關議題<ref name = "吳介民 01"/>，而美國希望能夠和平地討論<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140804140143/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-03-23/taiwan-riot-police-move-on-trade-protesters-in-cabinet-compound.html |title = Taiwan’s President to Meet Protesters Who Seized Legislature |author = Tim Culpan |date = 2014-03-25 |publisher = [[彭博社|彭博社]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  }}</ref>{{sfnm|吳叡人等|2016年|1loc=第130頁至第131頁}}。[[美國國會|美國國會]]{{Link-en|美國國會臺灣連線|Congressional Taiwan Caucus|臺灣連線}}創始成員、[[美國參議院|參議院]]議員[[謝羅德·布朗|謝羅德·布朗]]則敦促馬英九確保非暴力的和平解決<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2014/03/25/2003586494 |title = TRADE PACT SIEGE: Politicians, civic groups lash out over crackdown |author = Chris Wang |date = 2014-03-25 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502110408/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2014/03/25/2003586494 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

