在太陽花學運中，受到中華民國與[[日本|日本]]民間[[中華民國與日本關係|彼此友好]]的影響，亦有日本民眾表達對運動的支持<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/20/taiwan-japan-ties/ |title = Taiwan-Japan Ties In The Sunflower Movement |author =  |date = 2017-07-20 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-04-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220409043124/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/20/taiwan-japan-ties/ }}</ref>。在美國和[[英國|英國]]等地的[[海外臺灣人|海外臺灣人]]也先後發起示威，以支持這次學生運動<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2014/03/25/2003586476 |title = Taiwanese abroad show support |author = Tony Phillips |date = 2014-03-25 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502061808/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2014/03/25/2003586476 |dead-url = no }}</ref>{{sfnm|公民聲音團隊|2014年|1loc=第8頁|港千尋|2015年|2loc=第88頁}}。3月29日和3月30日，為了支持太陽花學運，21個國家中的50多個城市舉行海外團結集會<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2014/04/01/2003587023 |title = TRADE PACT SIEGE: Rallies held across globe for Sunflower movement |author = Jason Pan |date = 2014-04-01 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502110830/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2014/04/01/2003587023 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，這些活動主要由海外臺灣人組織<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/20/the-overseas-solidarity-movement/ |title = The Overseas Solidarity Movement |author =  |date = 2017-07-20 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523162315/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/20/the-overseas-solidarity-movement/ }}</ref>{{sfnm|公民聲音團隊|2014年|1loc=第8頁|港千尋|2015年|2loc=第244頁}}。4月3日，[[美國東亞暨太平洋事務助理國務卿|美國東亞暨太平洋事務助理國務卿]]{{Link-en|丹尼爾·R·羅素|Daniel R. Russel}}在美國參議院作證，表示強化與中華民國的[[中華民國與美國關係|關係]]、及與台灣人民的長期友誼，仍然是美國在{{Link-en|巴拉克·歐巴馬政府的東亞外交政策|East Asian foreign policy of the Barack Obama administration|亞太再平衡戰略}}的關鍵要素<ref name = "吳介民 01"/>{{sfnm|吳叡人等|2016年|1loc=第131頁}}。4月5日，波蘭媒體集團Niezalezna收到[[臺北經濟文化代表處|波蘭臺北辦事處]]有關報導的信件，抗議其將佔領行政院廣場的抗議者及隨後的警察暴力鎮壓，與佔領[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]]首都[[基輔|基輔]]市中心[[獨立廣場_(基輔)|獨立廣場]]的[[烏克蘭親歐盟示威運動|抗議者]]相提並論，這引發干涉[[新聞自由|新聞自由]]的爭議<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2014/04/06/2003587381 |title = Polish media asked to retract siege reporting |author = Loa Iok-sin |date = 2014-04-06 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502050005/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2014/04/06/2003587381 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

