在太陽花學運行動中，參與者對於法律有著較為靈活、甚至試圖重新定義法律的觀點<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/25/flexible-view-law/ |title = Did The Sunflower Movement Have A Flexible View Of The Law? |author =  |date = 2017-07-25 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-04-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220409205504/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/25/flexible-view-law/ }}</ref>，其強調運動正當性來自於人民利益是最高的法律，不過一開始也設定運動屬於[[非暴力|非暴力]]性質<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/24/sunflower-movement-violence/ |title = Why Was Violence Never On The Table During The Sunflower Movement? |author =  |date = 2017-07-24 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523161848/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/24/sunflower-movement-violence/ }}</ref>{{sfnm|劉定綱|2014年|1loc=第19頁|黃恐龍|2014年|2loc=第181頁至第182頁|港千尋|2015年|3loc=第39頁至第40頁、第88頁至第89頁|吳叡人等|2016年|4loc=第302頁至第323}}。在最早的佔領立法院行動中，有6人在抗議活動中遭到逮捕<ref name = "寇謐將 01"/>；而在佔領行政院的行動中，有61人遭到逮捕<ref name = "Lawrence Chung 01"/><ref name = "蘋果日報 01"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=96463 |title = 衝擊行政院學運領袖被羈押 |author =  |date = 2014-03-24 |publisher = [[now新聞台|now新聞台]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2018-12-11 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181211071037/https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=96463 |dead-url = no }}</ref>{{sfnm|晏山農等|2015年|1loc=第61頁}}。4月9日，針對反服貿民眾先前闖入行政院，[[行政院發言人|行政院發言人]][[孫立群|孫立群]]表示在檢察官偵結起訴後，行政院會提起民事求償訴訟，求償金額300萬元<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.taiwan.cn/xwzx/bwkx/201404/t20140409_5987178.htm |title = 反服贸活动中遭硬闯破坏 台“行政院”拟求偿300万 |author = 朱炼 |date = 2014-04-09 |publisher = 中國台灣網 |language = Zh-hans |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502094808/http://www.taiwan.cn/xwzx/bwkx/201404/t20140409_5987178.htm |dead-url = no }}</ref>。4月21日，林飛帆、陳為廷、[[黃國昌|黃國昌]]和其他4名運動主要成員，主動前往[[臺灣臺北地方檢察署|臺灣臺北地方檢察署]]，解釋在3月18日開始佔領立法院、以及3月23日佔領行政院期間發生的事情<ref name = "Liu Shi-yi 01">{{Cite web |url = http://focustaiwan.tw/news/asoc/201404210038.aspx |title = Key figures in student protests questioned by prosecutors |author = Liu Shi-yi和Christie Chen |date = 2015-04-21 |publisher = [[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502091703/http://focustaiwan.tw/news/asoc/201404210038.aspx |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name = "Rich Chang 01">{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2014/04/22/2003588591 |title = Prosecutors question protest leaders |author = Rich Chang |date = 2014-04-22 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502091625/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2014/04/22/2003588591 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

檢察官指控部分抗議者犯下數項罪行，例如妨礙執行公務等<ref name = "Liu Shi-yi 01"/><ref name = "Rich Chang 01"/>{{sfnm|吳叡人等|2016年|1loc=第365頁至第366頁}}。而律師[[顧立雄|顧立雄]]表示如果被起訴<ref name = "Rich Chang 01"/>，被告將提出無罪辯護<ref name = "Liu Shi-yi 01"/>。到了6月，檢察官和警方已經調查400多名抗議活動參與者<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2014/06/06/2003592098 |title = Legal authorities are ‘abusing powers’ |author = Alison Hsiao |date = 2014-06-06 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502074634/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2014/06/06/2003592098 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。2015年2月10日，臺灣臺北地方檢察署針對佔領立法院案、佔領行政院案、路過臺北市政府警察局中正第一分局案，共起訴119人{{sfnm|晏山農等|2015年|1loc=第331頁至第333頁|港千尋|2015年|2loc=第19頁|吳叡人等|2016年|3loc=第365頁至第366頁}}。同年5月，還有39名抗議者因為參與佔領行政院，被指控違法入侵<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://focustaiwan.tw/news/asoc/201505050030.aspx |title = Another 39 Sunflower Movement protesters indicted |author = Peggy Tsai和Scully Hsiao |date = 2015-05-05 |publisher = [[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502085006/http://focustaiwan.tw/news/asoc/201505050030.aspx |dead-url = no }}</ref>。此外，[[江宜樺內閣|江宜樺內閣]]還另外起訴126名參與行政院行動的抗議者<ref name = "Tai Ya-chen 01">{{Cite web |url = http://focustaiwan.tw/news/aipl/201605230010.aspx |title = Government changes course on Sunflower Movement protesters |author = Tai Ya-chen和Elizabeth Hsu |date = 2016-05-23 |publisher = [[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190306043618/http://focustaiwan.tw/news/aipl/201605230010.aspx |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name = "Stacy Hsu 01">{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2016/05/24/2003646979 |title = Cabinet drops charges against students |author = Stacy Hsu和Abraham Gerber |date = 2016-05-24 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190306043133/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2016/05/24/2003646979 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

到了2016年5月20日，新任總統[[蔡英文|蔡英文]]任命的行政院院長[[林全|林全]]，選擇放棄[[告訴乃論|告訴乃論]]的刑事指控<ref name = "Tai Ya-chen 01"/><ref name = "Stacy Hsu 01"/>，也是[[林全內閣|林全內閣]]首個政治決策<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201605235014.aspx |title = 行政院宣布 對太陽花學運人士撤告 |author = 戴雅真 |date = 2016-05-23 |publisher = [[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-07-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190707173157/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201605235014.aspx |dead-url = no }}</ref>。同年6月，[[臺灣臺北地方法院|臺灣臺北地方法院]]開始傳喚21名抗議者出庭，首先是被指控犯有多項罪名的陳為廷、黃國昌和林飛帆等人<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2016/06/15/2003648639 |title = Sunflower leaders to face justice system ‘head-on’ |author = Jason Pan |date = 2016-06-15 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502103631/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2016/06/15/2003648639 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。最後[[臺灣臺北地方檢察署|臺灣臺北地方檢察署]]依照煽動罪<ref name = "Elaine Hou 01"/>、妨害公務等多項罪名，起訴要角黃國昌、林飛帆、陳為廷等22人<ref name = "夏丽娟 01"/>。2017年3月，臺灣臺北地方法院判決陳為廷、黃國昌和林飛帆等22人的罪名並不成立<ref name = "Elaine Hou 01"/>，檢方隨後上訴<ref name = "夏丽娟 01"/>。2018年3月13日，[[臺灣高等法院|臺灣高等法院]]二審宣判駁回上訴，仍然維持原先地方法院判決，判決黃國昌等22人無罪<ref name = "夏丽娟 01"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201803135003.aspx |title = 太陽花占立法院二審 黃國昌等人無罪 |author =  |date = 2018-03-13 |publisher = [[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |language = zh-hant |access-date = 2022-06-03 |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523170109/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201803135003.aspx }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2018/03/14/2003689244 |title = High Court acquits protesters against China trade pact |author = Jason Pan |date = 2018-03-14 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-02-