在太陽花學運中，對於警察的討論態度介於許多極端之間<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/25/police-discourse/ |title = Discourse About Police Within The Sunflower Movement |author =  |date = 2017-07-25 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-04-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220409115112/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/25/police-discourse/ }}</ref>，並因為行政院的鎮壓行動而大幅轉變{{sfnm|黃恐龍|2014年|1loc=第183頁至第189頁}}。根據運動期間的報導，鎮暴警察和其他警員過度使用武力，包括運用[[水砲|水砲]]和警棍攻擊抗議者頭部等暴力行為<ref name = "寇謐將 02"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/24/police-violence-sunflower-movement/ |title = Police Violence In The Sunflower Movement |author =  |date = 2017-07-24 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523162309/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/24/police-violence-sunflower-movement/ }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160918092400/https://www.lagranepoca.com/archivo/31354-crece-tension-taiwan-despues-una-violenta-dispersion.html |title = Crece la tensión en Taiwán después de una violenta dispersión |author = Por Lu Chen |date = 2014-03-25 |publisher = 《[[大紀元時報|大紀元時報]]》 |language = es |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  }}</ref>{{sfnm|晏山農等|2015年|1loc=第59頁至第62頁、第64頁至第65頁|吳叡人等|2016年|2loc=第192頁}}。警方強制驅離的作法被批評是國家暴力<ref name = "民視新聞台 01"/>，[[台灣團結聯盟|台灣團結聯盟]]便將鎮暴警察的驅離比喻為臺灣版的[[六四事件|六四事件]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://tw.news.yahoo.com/鎮暴警強驅學生-台聯-台灣版的六四天安門-044650027.html |title = 鎮暴警強驅學生 台聯：台灣版的六四天安門！ |author = 康仁俊 |date = 2014-03-24 |publisher = [[雅虎新聞|雅虎新聞]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523161846/https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E9%8E%AE%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%BC%B7%E9%A9%85%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F-%E5%8F%B0%E8%81%AF-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%89%88%E7%9A%84%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%A9%E5%AE%89%E9%96%80-044650027.html }}</ref>{{sfnm|晏山農等|2015年|1loc=第61頁至第62頁、第65頁|吳叡人等|2016年|2loc=第192頁、第194頁、第202頁、第326頁至第330頁、第338頁至第344頁、第360頁至第365頁}}。而在行政院的驅離過程中，警方還曾經命令記者離開<ref name = "寇謐將 02">{{Cite web |url = https://thediplomat.com/2014/03/riot-police-crack-down-on-taiwanese-protesters/ |title = Riot Police Crack Down on Taiwanese Protesters |author = [[寇謐將|寇謐將]] |date = 2014-03-24 |publisher = 《[[外交家雜誌|外交家雜誌]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190307232055/https://thediplomat.com/2014/03/riot-police-crack-down-on-taiwanese-protesters/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>，甚至對媒體使用暴力<ref name = "Loa Iok-sin 01">{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2014/03/25/2003586496 |title = TRADE PACT SIEGE: Journalists accuse police of attacking them |author = Loa Iok-sin |date = 2014-03-25 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502090634/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2014/03/25/2003586496 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

早在3月24日，[[台灣新聞記者協會|台灣新聞記者協會]]便譴責警方侵犯新聞自由，並收到10多起襲擊媒體記者的通報<ref name = "Loa Iok-sin 01"/>。7月30日，23名受傷的抗議者以企圖謀殺、脅迫和造成身體傷害等罪名，向行政院院長江宜樺、內政部警政署署長王卓鈞、[[臺北市政府警察局|臺北市政府警察局]]局長[[黃昇勇|黃昇勇]]和中正第一分局分局長方仰寧提起訴訟<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2014/07/30/2003596235 |title = Premier to face court over evictions |author = Chang Wen-chuan和Jason Pan |date = 2014-07-30 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190306111514/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2014/07/30/2003596235 |dead-url = no }}</ref>{{sfnm|吳叡人等|2016年|1loc=第365頁至第366頁}}。隨後100多名示威者在法院外，要求江宜樺辭職<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2014/07/31/2003596311 |title = Premier in court over violent evictions |author = Loa Iok-sin |date = 2014-07-31 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190306043021/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2014/07/31/2003596311 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。同年8月，一名[[臺中市|臺中市]]警員因為在[[Facebook|Facebook]]上針對抗議者發表不當言論，被判處3個月有期徒刑，並支付罰金<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://focustaiwan.tw/news/asoc/201408270023.aspx |title = Policeman sentenced to 3 months in jail for cursing activists |author = Liao Ren-kai和Elizabeth Hsu |date = 2014-08-27 |publisher = [[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502051916/http://focustaiwan.tw/news/asoc/201408270023.aspx |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2015年8月，臺灣臺北地方法院裁定警方的行為違反《[[警械使用條例|警械使用條例]]》，並命令[[臺北市政府|臺北市政府]]向抗議者林明慧支付新臺幣30萬元<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2015/08/09/2003624923 |title = Teacher awarded compensation for Sunflower beating |author = Jason Pan |date = 2015-08-09 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502052307/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2015/08/09/2003624923 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。同年9月，代理其他30名抗議者的律師向臺北市政府陳情，要求賠償新臺幣1,000多萬元<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2015/09/16/2003627829 |title = Lawyers seek state violence payments |author = Hsiao Ting-fang |date = 2015-09-16 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502065839/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2015/09/16/2003627829 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 後續影響 ==
=== 兩岸關係 ===
[[File:2015_Ma–Xi_Meeting_06.jpg|thumb]]直到2015年才在[[新加坡|新加坡]]舉行[[兩岸領導人會面|兩岸領導人會面]]。]]

2014年4月16日，[[中華人民共和國國務院|中華人民共和國國務院]]批評學生的舉動破壞和妨礙海峽兩岸關係的和平發展進程<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140625061716/http://www.asahi.com/articles/ASG4J6G87G4JUHBI036.html |script-title = ja:中国政府、台湾立法院占拠の学生ら批判 |author = 林望 |date = 2014-04-16 |publisher = 《[[朝日新聞|朝日新聞]]》 |language = ja |accessdate = 2019-02-14 |quote =  }}</ref>。5月7日，[[中國共產黨中央委員會總書記|中國共產黨中央委員會總書記]][[習近平|習近平]]在與[[親民黨|親民黨]]主席[[宋楚瑜|宋楚瑜]]會面時<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/201405070129.aspx |title = 習近平：遏制台獨分裂不會動搖 |author = 鄭崇生 |date = 2014-05-07 |publisher = [[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190330104849/https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/201405070129.aspx |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.xinhuanet.com//politics/2014-05/07/c_1110577861.htm |title = 习近平：两岸一家亲 没有什么心结不能化解 |author = 陈键兴 |date = 2014-05-07 |publisher = [[新華網|新華網]] |language = Zh-hans |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190330104840/http://www.xinhuanet.com//politics/2014-05/07/c_1110577861.htm |dead-url = no }}</ref>，表示中國大陸與臺灣的經濟一體化是互利的，雙方都會取得正向的成果，而不應受到干擾<ref name = "Ben Blanchard 01">{{Cite web |url = https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-taiwan/chinas-xi-stresses-benefits-of-ties-after-taiwan-protests-idUSBREA4606D20140507 |title = China's Xi stresses benefits of ties after Taiwan protests |author = Ben Blanchard |date = 2014-05-07 |publisher = [[路透社|路透社]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190330104836/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-taiwan/chinas-xi-stresses-benefits-of-ties-after-taiwan-protests-idUSBREA4606D20140507 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。他還間接地回應太陽花學運，表示中華人民共和國想更了解臺灣人民所關切的事物<ref name = "Ben Blanchard 01"/>。宋楚瑜則敦促中華人民共和國政府對於臺灣的中間派和多元主義觀點更加寬容<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/1507001/were-listening-xi-jinping-says-taiwan |title = We're listening, Xi Jinping says to Taiwan |author = Lawrence Chung |date = 2014-05-08 |publisher = 《[[南華早報|南華早報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190330120527/https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/1507001/were-listening-xi-jinping-says-taiwan |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

5月21日，民進黨立法委員批評行政院大陸委員會將對《海峽兩岸服務貿易協議》不利的資訊列為密件，僅公佈其認為有利的資訊{{noteTag|在答覆質詢時，陸委會主任委員[[王郁琦|王郁琦]]表示密件資料只用於政府內部參考，[[中華民國經濟部|經濟部]]次長[[卓士昭|卓士昭]]亦認為學術界的研究只用於內部決策參考<ref name = "Loa Iok-sin 02"/>。不過兩位官員都未解釋只向公眾發布有利於政府立場的民意調查數據的原因<ref name = "Loa Iok-sin 02"/>。}}<ref name = "Loa Iok-sin 02">{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2014/05/22/2003590950 |title = MAC hiding unfavorable data: DPP |author = Loa Iok-sin |date = 2014-05-22 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190330120448/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2014/05/22/2003590950 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。6月9日，經濟部政務次長[[杜紫軍|杜紫軍]]證實自從4月以來，中華人民共和國政府已經凍結與中華民國政府的《[[海峽兩岸貨品貿易協議|海峽兩岸貨品貿易協議]]》談判，該協議原本預計在2014年底簽署<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://focustaiwan.tw/news/acs/201406090011.aspx |title = Trade-in-goods pact with China unlikely this year: official |author = Huang Chiao-wen和Y.F. Low |date = 2014-06-09 |publisher = [[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190330104854/http://focustaiwan.tw/news/acs/201406090011.aspx |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name = "Lawrence Chung 02">{{Cite web |url = https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/1528429/beijing-freezes-cooperation-talks-taiwan-over-stalled-trade-pact |title = Beijing ‘freezes’ cooperation talks with Taiwan over stalled trade pact |author = Lawrence Chung |date = 2014-06-10 |publisher = 《[[南華早報|南華早報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190330120647/https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/1528429/beijing-freezes-cooperation-talks-taiwan-over-stalled-trade-pact |dead-url = no }}</ref>。杜紫軍呼籲立法院盡快批准《海峽兩岸服務貿易協議》、及加強往後海峽兩岸協議審查的新法案，避免拖延後續《海峽兩岸貨品貿易協議》的談判，部分分析師亦認為凍結原因在於《海峽兩岸服務貿易協議》的僵局<ref name = "Lawrence Chung 02"/>。馬英九對此曾敦促在立法院有所進展<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://focustaiwan.tw/news/acs/201406090008.aspx |title = Talks with China suspended on stalled services pact |author = Kelven Huang、Huang Chiao-wen和Y.F. Low |date = 2014-06-09 |publisher = [[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190330120416/http://focustaiwan.tw/news/acs/201406090008.aspx |dead-url = no }}</ref>，而後者也在6月13日召開特別會議<ref name = "Lawrence Chung 02"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2014/06/10/2003592396 |title = Economics ministry urges action on cross-strait trade |author = Helen Ku |date = 2014-06-10 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190330104845/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2014/06/10/2003592396 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

而在太陽花學運過後，海峽兩岸的執政雙方仍試圖影響臺灣社會<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/25/kmt-china-intervention/ |title = Attempts By The KMT And China To Intervene After The Movement? |author =  |date = 2017-07-25 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190330162726/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/25/kmt-china-intervention/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。不過受到這次佔領運動的影響，除了使中華民國政府放緩與中華人民共和國政府的談判外<ref name = "Francisco Luis Pérez 01"/>，後者促進中國統一的路線也被迫重新調整<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140417073948/http://www.jiji.com/jc/c?g=int_30&rel=j7&k=2014041600783 |script-title = ja:台湾戦略、仕切り直し＝立法院占拠受け－中国 |author =  |date = 2014-04-16 |publisher = [[時事通信社|時事通信社]] |language = ja |accessdate = 2019-02-14 |quote =  }}</ref>{{sfnm|吳叡人等|2016年|1loc=第108頁至第109頁、第155頁至第156頁}}。直到6月25日，為了重建太陽花學運後的海峽兩岸關係，大陸國務院臺灣事務辦公室主任[[張志軍|張志軍]]抵達臺灣，除了進行為期4天的訪問外，亦與陸委會主任委員[[王郁琦|王郁琦]]舉行[[王張會|會談]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140626012831/http://time.com/2919774/china-sends-1st-minister-level-official-to-taiwan/ |title = China’s First Minister-Level Official Visits Taiwan |author = [[美聯社|美聯社]] |date = 2014-06-25 |publisher = 《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  }}</ref>{{sfnm|港千尋|2015年|1loc=第248頁}}。

