在太陽花學運期間及之後，許多學生運動者、青年運動者動組成各種社團組織<ref name="#1"/>，這次運動也促成臺灣公民社會的復興<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://thediplomat.com/2014/07/was-taiwans-sunflower-movement-successful/ |title = Was Taiwan’s Sunflower Movement Successful? |author = [[寇謐將|寇謐將]] |date = 2014-07-01 |publisher = 《[[外交家雜誌|外交家雜誌]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190307231543/https://thediplomat.com/2014/07/was-taiwans-sunflower-movement-successful/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>{{sfnm|晏山農等|2015年|1loc=第328頁、第410頁至第411頁}}。例如學生社團在3月31日串連成立民主黑潮學生聯盟、及號召罷免國民黨立法委員後，後續的割闌尾計畫在2014年4月下旬繼續推動，並規劃到各地立法委員選舉區進一步行動<ref name = "赵雪晨 01"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/25/the-appendectomy-project/ |title = The Appendectomy Project |author =  |date = 2017-07-25 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523214755/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/25/the-appendectomy-project/ }}</ref>{{sfnm|劉定綱|2014年|1loc=第25頁|公民聲音團隊|2014年|2loc=第14頁至第15頁|晏山農等|2015年|3loc=第109頁至第111頁、第114頁、第121頁至第122頁、第128頁至第129頁、第133頁至第134頁、第338頁、第410頁至第411頁|港千尋|2015年|4loc=第248頁|吳叡人等|2016年|5loc=第196頁至第198頁}}。5月18日，林飛帆、陳為廷和黃國昌組成一個新的組織──[[島國前進|島國前進]]<ref name = "Wen Kuei-hsiang 01">{{Cite web |url = http://focustaiwan.tw/news/asoc/201405180012.aspx |title = Student protesters form new group to tackle referendum rules |author = Wen Kuei-hsiang和Jeffrey Wu |date = 2014-05-18 |publisher = [[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502085520/http://focustaiwan.tw/news/asoc/201405180012.aspx |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2015/03/11/2003613266 |title = Referendum Act reform petition to enter phase II |author = Lii Wen |date = 2015-03-11 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502073305/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2015/03/11/2003613266 |dead-url = no }}</ref>{{sfnm|晏山農等|2015年|1loc=第410頁|港千尋|2015年|2loc=第248頁}}。該組織的目的是推動公民投票改革、《海峽兩岸服務貿易協議》的立法審查，以及監督其他海峽兩岸協議與經濟法案<ref name = "Wen Kuei-hsiang 01"/>{{sfnm|晏山農等|2015年|1loc=第410頁}}。

太陽花學運也影響著往後其他許多議題事件<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/06/22/other-afterlives-of-the-movement/ |title = Other Afterlives Of The Movement? |author =  |date = 2017-06-22 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523162314/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/06/22/other-afterlives-of-the-movement/ }}</ref>，並擴散成各種抗爭{{sfnm|黃恐龍|2014年|1loc=第289頁至第319頁|港千尋|2015年|2loc=第246頁至第249頁}}。其中著名的社會運動人士[[音地大帝|音地大帝]]在參與太陽花學運後，另外發想出「大腸花論壇」活動，後來更成立防止國家權力擴大的「[[公民攝影守護民主陣線|公民攝影守護民主陣線]]」<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/24/indie-dadee/ |title = Indie DaDee |author =  |date = 2017-07-24 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523174737/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/24/indie-dadee/ }}</ref>{{sfnm|公民聲音團隊|2014年|1loc=第16頁|黃恐龍|2014年|2loc=第112頁至第113頁、第290頁至第295頁|晏山農等|2015年|3loc=第129頁至第131頁、第185頁至第186頁、第290頁至第300頁、第411頁|港千尋|2015年|4loc=第245頁}}。到了4月，隨著[[林義雄|林義雄]]針對停建[[龍門核能發電廠|龍門核能發電廠]]發起絕食，引發社會再次發起「停建核四、還權於民」抗爭行動<ref name = "executive-yuan-outrage 01"/>{{sfnm|黃恐龍|2014年|1loc=第307頁至第310頁|港千尋|2015年|2loc=第40頁、第246頁至第247頁|吳叡人等|2016年|3loc=第41頁至第42頁}}。4月27日，反核團體[[佔領忠孝西路事件|佔領忠孝西路]]<ref name = "中央研究院 02"/>{{sfnm|黃恐龍|2014年|1loc=第310頁至第313頁|港千尋|2015年|2loc=第247頁}}。而在4月28日凌晨，警方出動鎮暴水車強制驅離忠孝西路上的抗議民眾<ref name = "中央研究院 02"/>{{sfnm|黃恐龍|2014年|1loc=第314頁至第319頁|港千尋|2015年|2loc=第247頁}}。另外在6月27日，趁著張志軍訪問臺灣，抗議人士在[[高雄市|高雄市]][[西子灣|西子灣]]向其潑漆[[張志軍訪臺爭議與衝突|抗議]]<ref name = "中央研究院 02"/>{{sfnm|港千尋|2015年|1loc=第248頁}}。

同年8月，由數名學生運動領導人所組成的代表團前往美國，與美國國會、美國國務院和[[美國在台協會|美國在台協會]]人員會面<ref name = "William Lowther 01">{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2014/08/23/2003598054 |title = Sunflower leaders urge US to drop ‘one China’ policy |author = William Lowther |date = 2014-08-23 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502051155/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2014/08/23/2003598054 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。其中，林飛帆表示太陽花學運拒絕「[[一個中國|一個中國]]」政策，並認為如果馬英九[[馬習會_(2014年)|會見]]習近平的話，將會再次出現抗議活動<ref name = "William Lowther 01"/>。而自從太陽花學運以來，人們看到試圖佔領立法院的政治示威運動急劇增加，主要是希望藉此讓議題能在臺灣社會獲得廣泛的知名度，包括2015年的[[反高中課綱微調運動|反高中課綱微調運動]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/25/legislative-yuan-attempts/ |title = Attempts To Occupy The Legislative Yuan Following The Sunflower Movement? |author =  |date = 2017-07-25 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190330162815/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/25/legislative-yuan-attempts/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>{{sfnm|吳叡人等|2016年|1loc=第369頁至第370頁}}。在太陽花學運之後，許多青年亦前往地方創建社會企業，也出現反觀光的[[原住民青年陣線聯盟|原住民青年陣線聯盟]]、[[馬太攻守聯盟|馬太攻守聯盟]]、[[母語自救路過團|母語自救路過團]]等原住民族運動{{sfnm|吳叡人等|2016年|1loc=第244頁至第261頁、第386頁至第388頁}}。

=== 選舉結果 ===
[[File:時代力量立委候選人林昶佐_05.JPG|thumb]]與[[時代力量|時代力量]]先後崛起。]]

太陽花學運也讓部分人開始嘗試投入選舉政治<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/24/activists-enter-electoral-politics/ |title = What Led Activists To Enter Electoral Politics After The Sunflower Movement? |author =  |date = 2017-07-24 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-30 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190330162742/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/24/activists-enter-electoral-politics/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>{{sfnm|吳叡人等|2016年|1loc=第78頁、第109頁至第110頁}}。而隨著年輕世代引起臺灣民眾的注意，臺灣政治人物之後都試圖去吸引青年投票<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/26/politicians-youth-vote/ |title = Politicians Attempting To Capture The Youth Vote After The Sunflower Movement |author =  |date = 2017-07-26 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220525223426/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/26/politicians-youth-vote/ }}</ref>。在2014年11月29日的[[2014年中華民國地方公職人員選舉|地方公職人員選舉]]，執政的國民黨遭遇重大的挫折<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-taiwan-idUSKBN0NP0AR20150504 |title = China's Xi calls for 'equal' political talks with Taiwan |author = Ben Blanchard |date = 2015-05-04 |publisher = [[路透社|路透社]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502084500/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-taiwan-idUSKBN0NP0AR20150504 |dead-url = no }}</ref>{{sfnm|吳叡人等|2016年|1loc=第41頁至第42頁、第78頁、第109頁至第110頁、第156頁至第157頁、第203頁}}。這導致馬英九辭去國民黨主席，江宜樺亦辭去行政院院長<ref name = "中央研究院 02"/><ref name = "楊虔豪 01">{{Cite web |url = https://toyokeizai.net/articles/-/54961 |script-title = ja:｢中国への嫌悪感｣が台湾民進党圧勝の背景 |author = [[楊虔豪|楊虔豪]] |date = 2014-12-04 |publisher = [[東洋經濟新報社|東洋經濟新報社]] |language = ja |accessdate = 2019-02-14 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502102714/https://toyokeizai.net/articles/-/54961 |dead-url = no }}</ref>{{sfnm|晏山農等|2015年|1loc=第326頁}}。對於這次選舉的結果，學生和社會團體的動員被視為原因之一<ref name = "Francisco Luis Pérez 01"/><ref name = "楊虔豪 01"/>。而儘管林飛帆表示從自己的角色出發分析並不合適，但仍認為國民黨的失敗確實是受到太陽花學運的強烈影響<ref name = "楊虔豪 01"/>。

[[英國廣播公司|英國廣播公司]]則評論表示，這場運動可能促成臺灣進一步的民主化，並且讓人民來決定臺灣的命運，而不再是依靠過往的政黨<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-26743794 |title = What unprecedented protest means for Taiwan |author = Cindy Sui |date = 2014-03-26 |publisher = [[英國廣播公司新聞網|英國廣播公司新聞網]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-01-13 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190113072909/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-26743794 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。而為了接續這場運動，則有[[時代力量|時代力量]]和[[社會民主黨_(臺灣)|社會民主黨]]這兩個政黨在臺灣成立，同樣支持參與式民主、反對大企業與政府利益勾結等<ref name = "Francisco Luis Pérez 01"/>，且部分參與者還先後投入選舉<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://theinitium.com/article/20160117-taiwan-legislator-election/ |title = 太陽花政黨：2014闖進立法院，2016選進去 |author = 蔣金和林揚軼 |date = 2016-01-17 |publisher = [[端傳媒|端傳媒]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-04-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190404071018/https://theinitium.com/article/20160117-taiwan-legislator-election/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>{{sfnm|晏山農等|2015年|1loc=第328頁}}。其中在2015年，部分太陽花學運的成員共同組成時代力量<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2015/09/14/2003627680 |title = New Power Party announces leadership structure |author = Chen Wei-han |date = 2015-09-14 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-04-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190404101225/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/taiwan/archives/2015/09/14/2003627680 |dead-url = no }}</ref>，倡導人權保障、[[公民自由|公民自由]]和[[政治自由|政治自由]]、以及國家獨立<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.newpowerparty.tw/policy |title = 政策/政見 |author =  |date =  |publisher = [[時代力量|時代力量]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190327162857/https://www.newpowerparty.tw/policy |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://qz.com/596669/taiwans-newest-politicians-include-a-rock-star-and-an-aboriginal-activist/ |title = Taiwan’s newest politicians include a rock star and an aboriginal activist |author = Josh Horwitz |date = 2016-01-18 |publisher = [[Quartz_(媒體)|Quartz]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-04-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190404101347/https://qz.com/596669/taiwans-newest-politicians-include-a-rock-star-and-an-aboriginal-activist/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

不過在2015年年2月舉行的[[2015年苗栗縣第二選舉區立法委員缺額補選|立法委員補選]]，太陽花學運領導人之一的陳為廷由於被媒體報導其性騷擾的過去而遭到批評<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.sankei.com/world/news/141224/wor1412240029-n1.html |script-title = ja:補選出馬表明の学生運動指導者に痴漢の過去　台湾で波紋広がる |author = 田中靖人 |date = 2015-02-25 |publisher = 《[[產經新聞|產經新聞]]》 |language = ja |accessdate = 2019-02-14 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502095454/https://www.sankei.com/world/news/141224/wor1412240029-n1.html |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name = "田中靖人 01">{{Cite web |url = https://www.sankei.com/world/news/141225/wor1412250032-n1.html |script-title = ja:「痴漢」告白の台湾学生指導者、出馬取りやめ |author = 田中靖人 |date = 2015-02-25 |publisher = 《[[產經新聞|產經新聞]]》 |language = ja |accessdate = 2019-02-14 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502103433/https://www.sankei.com/world/news/141225/wor1412250032-n1.html |dead-url = no }}</ref>；最後其坦承此事，並在2月25日宣布退出選舉<ref name = "田中靖人 01"/>。而受到太陽花學運的部分影響，蔡英文和其帶領的民進黨在2016年的[[2016年中華民國總統選舉|總統選舉]]和[[2016年中華民國立法委員選舉|立法委員選舉]]亦[[2016年中華民國總統副總統及立法委員選舉|獲得成功]]，蔡英文成為中華民國首位女性總統，民進黨重返執政及首度完全執政<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/26/2016-electoral-successes/ |title = 2016 Electoral Successes A Result Of The Sunflower Movement? |author =  |date = 2017-07-26 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523152429/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/26/2016-electoral-successes/ }}</ref>{{sfnm|吳叡人等|2016年|1loc=第78頁、第156頁至第157頁、第203頁}}。時代力量在立法委員選舉部分與民進黨合作<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://mainichi.jp/articles/20160107/k00/00m/030/030000c |script-title = ja:台湾・立法院選「時代力量」に勢い…与党地盤で善戦 |author = 鈴木玲子 |date = 2016-01-16 |publisher = 《[[每日新聞|每日新聞]]》 |language = ja |accessdate = 2019-02-14 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502081928/http://mainichi.jp/articles/20160107/k00/00m/030/030000c |dead-url = no }}</ref>，最後總共獲得5個立法院[[第9屆中華民國立法委員名單|席次]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2016/01/17/2003637386 |title = ELECTIONS: DPP secures absolute majority in Legislative Yuan |author = Alison Hsiao |date = 2016-01-17 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502085657/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2016/01/17/2003637386 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://thediplomat.com/2016/02/taiwans-third-force-makes-its-presence-known-in-legislature/ |title = Taiwan's 'Third Force' Makes Its Presence Known in Legislature |author = Linda van der Horst |date = 2014-03-20 |publisher = 《[[外交家雜誌|外交家雜誌]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502085719/https://thediplomat.com/2016/02/taiwans-third-force-makes-its-presence-known-in-legislature/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>{{sfnm|吳叡人等|2016年|1loc=第203頁}}。同年，曾經參與太陽花學運的公民黑客[[唐鳳|唐鳳]]被任命為[[政務委員_(中華民國)|政務委員]]，也是中華民國首位跨性別官員<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.elconfidencial.com/tecnologia/2016-09-03/la-hacker-transgenero-que-ha-revolucionado-el-gobierno-taiwanes_1254559/ |title = La 'hacker' superdotada y transgénero que ha revolucionado el gobierno taiwanés |author = Barbara Celis |date = 2016-09-03 |publisher = 《[[機密報|機密報]]》 |language = es |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502082514/https://www.elconfidencial.com/tecnologia/2016-09-03/la-hacker-transgenero-que-ha-revolucionado-el-gobierno-taiwanes_1254559/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 流行文化 ===
[[File:01.01_中華民國106年元旦總統府升旗音樂會中,滅火器樂團的演出_(32015297125).jpg|thumb]]在[[總統府_(臺灣)|總統府]]升旗音樂會中演出。]]

早在太陽花學運之前，運動者的「亞文化」發展有助於運動者家發展其公共領域<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/08/10/activist-subculture/ |title = Activist Subculture |author =  |date = 2017-08-10 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523180714/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/08/10/activist-subculture/ }}</ref>。隨著臺灣青年活動的興起，臺灣出現許多服裝品牌，這些品牌商品在運動者間很受歡迎，並表達有關臺灣民間社會認可的政治訊息<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/20/activist-merchandise/ |title = Activist Merchandise |author =  |date = 2017-07-20 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523214758/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/20/activist-merchandise/ }}</ref>。部分書籍和電影在運動者亞文化中很受歡迎<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/20/activist-books-films/ |title = Books And Film Popular Among Activists |author =  |date = 2017-07-20 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220525223427/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/20/activist-books-films/ }}</ref>，部分咖啡館、住宅和書店也是青年運動者的聚會場所<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/20/coffee-bookstores-live-houses/ |title = Activist Coffee Shops, Live Houses, and Bookstores |author =  |date = 2017-07-20 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523162309/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/20/coffee-bookstores-live-houses/ }}</ref>，某些臺北市頻繁發生抗議空間亦是成員聚會的地點<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/25/frequent-protest-spaces-in-taipei/ |title = Frequent Protest Spaces In Taipei |author =  |date = 2017-07-25 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220525204400/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/25/frequent-protest-spaces-in-taipei/ }}</ref>。而自從學運以後，「黑箱」已經成為臺灣社會常用的詞彙<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/20/what-was-the-black-box/ |title = What Was The “Black Box” And Why Were Occupiers Opposed To It? |author =  |date = 2017-07-20 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523161849/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/20/what-was-the-black-box/ }}</ref>{{sfnm|黃恐龍|2014年|1loc=第34頁|港千尋|2015年|2loc=第95頁至第98頁、第106頁至第115頁}}。同時，鹿茸、香蕉、太陽餅也成為群眾嘲諷的對象，更有網友創意團購太陽餅、「伏冒」（感冒藥）送去行政院<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://tw.news.appledaily.com/politics/realtime/20140325/366667 |title = 太陽餅過時囉！　現在買伏冒送政院正夯 |author = 胡治言 |date = 2014-03-25 |publisher = 《[[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果日報]]》 |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2020-05-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200507011123/https://tw.news.appledaily.com/politics/realtime/20140325/366667 }}</ref>{{sfnm|公民聲音團隊|2014年|1loc=第9頁|黃恐龍|2014年|2loc=第190頁至第193頁|港千尋|2015年|3loc=第240頁、第242頁至第243頁}}。

而一些[[獨立音樂|獨立樂團]]和藝術家創作有關社會問題的歌曲，同樣在臺灣青年運動者中贏得許多觀眾，包括[[拷秋勤|拷秋勤]]樂團創作的《官逼民反》等{{Sfnm|公民聲音團隊|2014年|1loc=第5頁}}<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/20/activist-artists-and-bands/ |title = Activist Artists and Bands |author =  |date = 2017-07-20 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523170111/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/20/activist-artists-and-bands/ }}</ref>。而太陽花學運的運動代表曲，則是由[[滅火器樂團|滅火器樂團]]主唱[[楊大正|楊大正]]為運動創作的歌曲《[[島嶼天光|島嶼天光]]》<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://focustaiwan.tw/news/aipl/201404100034.aspx |title = Festive rally closes Legislature occupation as protesters head home |author = Chen Chih-chung和Elaine Hou |date = 2014-04-10 |publisher = [[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-08-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190828123240/http://focustaiwan.tw/news/aipl/201404100034.aspx |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://thediplomat.com/2014/04/sunflowers-end-occupation-of-taiwans-legislature/ |title = Sunflowers End Occupation of Taiwan’s Legislature |author = [[寇謐將|寇謐將]] |date = 2014-04-11 |publisher = 《[[外交家雜誌|外交家雜誌]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-03-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190307232523/https://thediplomat.com/2014/04/sunflowers-end-occupation-of-taiwans-legislature/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>{{Sfnm|公民聲音團隊|2014年|1loc=第10頁|港千尋|2015年|2loc=第243頁至第244頁|黃恐龍|2014年|3loc=第195頁至第198頁|晏山農等|2015年|4loc=第81頁至第82頁|港千尋|2015年|5loc=第83頁至第85頁、第87頁、第192頁至第193頁}}。3月27日，他在立法院現場教唱、錄音錄影，之後由臺灣的藝術大學學生製作成兩部音樂影片，並在網際網路上傳播{{Sfnm|公民聲音團隊|2014年|1loc=第10頁晏山農等|2015年|2loc=第81頁至第82頁|港千尋|2015年|3loc=第83頁、第243頁至第244頁}}。到了3月31日，滅火器樂團便在遊行中演唱《島嶼天光》，並播放在立法院拍攝製作的音樂影片{{Sfnm|公民聲音團隊|2014年|1loc=第11頁|黃恐龍|2014年|2loc=第195頁至第196頁|晏山農等|2015年|3loc=第91頁}}。另外在3月21日，[[施明德|施明德]]女兒[[施蜜娜|施蜜娜]]在議場內部學生同意下，在議場外牆上噴寫「[[當獨裁成為事實，革命就是義務|當獨裁成為事實，革命就是義務]]」{{Sfnm|公民聲音團隊|2014年|1loc=第7頁|晏山農等|2015年|2loc=第44頁}}。

在太陽花學運中，許多藝術家也反對《海峽兩岸服務貿易協議》，同時存在著許多表達訴求、詆毀攻擊、挪用戲仿、呈現共同記憶的藝術創作<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/25/art-sunflower-movement/ |title = Art and the Sunflower Movement |author =  |date = 2017-07-24 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523162310/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/25/art-sunflower-movement/ }}</ref>，這包括創意海報、各式照片、版畫等作品{{sfnm|黃恐龍|2014年|1loc=第18頁至第22頁、第114頁至第176頁、第228頁至第232頁|晏山農等|2015年|2loc=第183頁至第184頁|港千尋|2015年|3loc=第13頁、第15頁、第92頁至第94頁、第208頁至第219頁|吳叡人等|2016年|4loc=第138頁至第139頁}}。4月1日，[[郝明義|郝明義]]在Facebook上發起「100人的太陽花」聲援行動，號召藝術家以創作發聲，並引起熱烈迴響{{Sfnm|公民聲音團隊|2014年|1loc=第12頁}}。到了4月6日，郝明義與藝文界人士召開記者會，公布6天來蒐集到的150件太陽花學運作品{{Sfnm|公民聲音團隊|2014年|1loc=第15頁}}。「太陽花學運」還被視為美學與政治的實踐案例，並在同年和「大腸花論壇」入圍[[台新藝術獎|台新藝術獎]]提名{{sfnm|晏山農等|2015年|1loc=第290頁至第291頁|吳叡人等|2016年|2loc=第373頁至第383頁}}。

== 運動評價 ==
[[File:Hong_Kong_Umbrella_Revolution_-umbrellarevolution_-UmbrellaMovement_(15292823874).jpg|thumb]]爆發[[雨傘革命|雨傘革命]]。]]

太陽花學運是一個結構複雜的運動，參與主體與訴求相當複雜多元<ref name = "吳介民 01"/>{{sfnm|晏山農等|2015年|1loc=第320頁至第324頁|吳叡人等|2016年|2loc=第126頁至第127頁}}。而作為一場抗議活動，太陽花學運是深深影響著臺灣社會的歷史事件之一<ref name = "Francisco Luis Pérez 01"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/15/sunflower-movement-significance/ |title = What Was The Significance Of The Sunflower Movement? |author =  |date = 2017-07-15 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-04-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220409043126/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/15/sunflower-movement-significance/ }}</ref>，也是[[中華民國歷史|中華民國歷史]]上首次發生立法院議場遭到民眾佔領<ref name = "比嘉清太 03"/><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://archive.is/20140319044548/http://news.rti.org.tw/index_newsContent.aspx?nid=492136#selection-829.1-832.0 |title = 群眾占領議場 國會史上首次 |author = 陳沂庭 |date = 2014-03-19 |publisher = [[中央廣播電臺|中央廣播電臺]] |language = Zh-hant |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2014-03-19/taiwan-students-occupy-legislature-over-china-trade-pact-vote |title = Taiwan Students Occupy Legislature Over China Pact |author = Adela Lin和Tim Culpan |date = 2014-03-19 |publisher = [[彭博社|彭博社]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502142923/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2014-03-19/taiwan-students-occupy-legislature-over-china-trade-pact-vote |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/1740013/one-year-impact-sunflower-movement-protests-taiwan-continue-blossom |title = One year on: impact of ‘sunflower’ movement protests in Taiwan continues to blossom |author = [[法新社|法新社]] |date = 2015-03-01 |publisher = 《[[南華早報|南華早報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502080637/https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/1740013/one-year-impact-sunflower-movement-protests-taiwan-continue-blossom |dead-url = no }}</ref>{{sfnm|劉定綱|2014年|1loc=第16頁|黃恐龍|2014年|2loc=第5頁|晏山農等|2015年|3loc=第324頁至第330頁}}。而從動員的角度觀察，這是從1980年代啟動民主化以來，最大強度的「[[公民不服從|公民不服從]]」集體行動。<ref name = "吳介民 01"/>。雖然其影響難以量化，但許多人的報告表示在太陽花學運之後，臺灣的社會氛圍發生變化<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/11/13/social-atmosphere-changes/ |title = What Changed About The Social Atmosphere In Taiwan After The Sunflower Movement? |author =  |date = 2017-11-13 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523162310/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/11/13/social-atmosphere-changes/ }}</ref>。黃國昌和陳為廷都把這次運動視為臺灣政治的「第三勢力」，林飛帆亦強調這場運動完全獨立於國民黨或民進黨<ref name = "William Lowther 01"/>{{sfnm|吳叡人等|2016年|1loc=第78頁}}。

許多參與太陽花學運的年輕人，過去在日常生活中曾感到在政治上已經失去權力，但在運動之後突然擁有控制自己命運的感覺<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/24/everyday-rupture/ |title = Why Did The Sunflower Movement Rupture The Everyday For Many Participants? |author =  |date = 2017-07-24 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523174737/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/24/everyday-rupture/ }}</ref>{{sfnm|吳叡人等|2016年|1loc=第107頁至第108頁、第157頁至第160頁、第369頁至第370頁}}。而作為標誌著一代人成熟的事件，太陽花學運也造成不小的世代衝突<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/06/10/generational-conflict/ |title = Generational Conflict And The Sunflower Movement |author =  |date = 2017-06-10 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523170109/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/06/10/generational-conflict/ }}</ref>{{sfnm|吳叡人等|2016年|1loc=第107頁至第108頁}}。此外，許多太陽花學運的運動者堅持進步的左翼政治立場，這一事實對年輕人的政治觀點發展具有重要意義<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/26/progressive-politics/ |title = The Left Political Vision Of The Sunflower Movement? |author =  |date = 2017-07-26 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523182233/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/26/progressive-politics/ }}</ref>。2014年9月20日，[[唐獎|唐獎]]獲獎人[[余英時|余英時]]在演講中表達對該運動的支持，其讚賞學生的意圖，並認為民主社會的公民都應該用其選票抵制政府<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2014/09/21/2003600203 |title = Tang Prize’s Yu praises Sunflower protests |author = [[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |date = 2014-09-21 |publisher = 《[[台北時報|台北時報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502060809/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/front/archives/2014/09/21/2003600203 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。而包括[[埃里克·奧林·賴特|埃里克·奧林·賴特]]、[[子安宣邦|子安宣邦]]等重要學者都曾觀察太陽花學運，而[[吳叡人|吳叡人]]則提出《黑潮論》說法{{sfnm|晏山農等|2015年|1loc=第97頁至第98頁、第102頁|吳叡人等|2016年|2loc=第19頁、第25頁至第50頁}}。

太陽花學運的最後階段與結束方式，對後來的運動方式產生很大影響<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/11/13/movement-endgame/ |title = The Endgame Of The Movement |author =  |date = 2017-11-13 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523152430/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/11/13/movement-endgame/ }}</ref>，甚至被認為是啟發2014年的香港[[雨傘革命|雨傘革命]]、2015年的日本[[自由民主主義學生緊急行動|自由民主主義學生緊急行動]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2015/10/151001_hk_occupy_anniversary_taiwan_view |title = 台灣學運領袖陳為廷談「佔中」一週年：「香港太難了」 |author = 劉子維 |date = 2015-10-01 |publisher = [[英國廣播公司新聞網|英國廣播公司新聞網]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502114708/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/china/2015/10/151001_hk_occupy_anniversary_taiwan_view |dead-url = no }}</ref>{{sfnm|公民聲音團隊|2014年|1loc=第16頁|晏山農等|2015年|2loc=第193頁至第194頁、第324頁至第326頁|吳叡人等|2016年|3loc=第156頁、第264頁至第265頁}}、及2019年的香港[[反修例運動|反修例運動]]。不過許多傳播媒體對於太陽花學運的報導，都集中在被視為運動主要領導者的林飛帆和陳為廷兩人身上，這也被認為是促成個人主義<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://focustaiwan.tw/news/aipl/201403310016.aspx |title = Activist profiles: the leaders of the Sunflower Student Movement |author = John Scot Feng |date = 2014-03-31 |publisher = [[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502082515/http://focustaiwan.tw/news/aipl/201403310016.aspx |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.wsj.com/articles/young-protesters-shaking-up-taiwans-china-policy-1396351842 |title = Young Protesters Shaking Up Taiwan's China Policy |author = Jenny W. Hsu |date = 2014-04-01 |publisher = 《[[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]]》 |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2019-05-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190502053156/https://www.wsj.com/articles/young-protesters-shaking-up-taiwans-china-policy-1396351842 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/24/personalism-leadership/ |title = Personalism and Leadership in the Sunflower Movement |author =  |date = 2017-07-24 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523214757/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/24/personalism-leadership/ }}</ref>，甚至後來還有對學生領袖的「告白牆」{{sfnm|黃恐龍|2014年|1loc=第237頁至第245頁|晏山農等|2015年|2loc=第105頁、第325頁}}。在整個運動過程中，立法院領中央導層必須解決一系列問題，其長期的主要挑戰是在公眾眼中維護運動的合法性，但也因而遭到各式批評<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/11/14/sunflower-central-leadership/ |title = Criticisms Of The Central Leadership In The Legislative Yuan |author =  |date = 2017-11-14 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220525223426/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/11/14/sunflower-central-leadership/ }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/24/movement-legitimacy/ |title = Maintaining The Legitimacy Of The Movement |author =  |date = 2017-07-24 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220523162310/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/07/24/movement-legitimacy/ }}</ref>{{sfnm|晏山農等|2015年|1loc=第320頁至第322頁}}。與此同時，運動中的部份內部爭論異議，被批評為與具體的政治分歧無關，而是在某種程度上成為社會資本的鬥爭<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/06/10/internal-dissent/ |title = Internal Dissent Within The Movement |author =  |date = 2017-06-10 |publisher = Daybreak Project |language = en |accessdate = 2019-03-01 |quote =  |archive-date = 2022-05-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220525204357/https://daybreak.newbloommag.net/2017/06/10/internal-dissent/ }}</ref>{{sfnm|晏山農等|2015年|1loc=第325頁}}。

